   ------- HELP    --------
  exit               : exit form the command mode.
  help               : description accessible commands.
  setsn              : set serial number, it describes slave/master
  sysinfo            : system information
  show               : show object [0..10] values
  logout             : logout all slave modules from system
  flash              : flash memory info
  fconfig            : show / set config table
  save               : save to flash config table
  showan             : show value 5000 - test procedure
  slave              : Show slave variables
  master             : Show master variables
  config             : Show config variables
  motor              : Show motor variables
  duty               : set manual duty value.
  r                  : run duty.
  h                  : halt duty.
  value              : show values in SCRU table.
  dg                 : Display debugger values
